      "text": [
        " \"لاَ هُوَ حَرَامٌ إِلاَّ أَنْ يُرِيدُوا ذَلِكَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3811 - Sama'ah asked Abu Abdullah (as) about two slave brothers, whether they can be separated, and about a woman and her child, whether they can be separated.\nImam (as) replied: \"No, it is forbidden, except if they themselves desire it.\""
        ]
      }
